@MindSculptor : yes, you could storm twice with [Dragonstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dragonstorm), if the spells are all activating on your upkeep, you choose the order. So choose [Dragonstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dragonstorm) first, then the other two so they'll resolve first, and you'll get your 3 dragons!  

@MechaKraken : yes, you have to exile suspended cards face-up. even if the card itself says "exile (or suspend) this card face-down", since you're using Jhoira's ability, and not the cards actual suspending rules.  

@LeoKula : i know, right??? too bad [Emrakul](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Emrakul) was just banned for EDH play, he was gonna make a killer addition to my Jhoira deck.... oh well, still have every other Eldrazi
